<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Selamat Datang di Toko Jaket Keren</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* CSS Variables - For consistent and easy theme management */
        :root {
            --primary-text-color: #ffffff;
            --button-login-bg: #28a745;
            --button-register-bg: #007bff;
            --overlay-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); /* Slightly darker overlay for better contrast */
            --shadow-subtle: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Refined shadow */
            --border-radius-card: 10px; /* Slightly smaller for cleaner look */
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?jacket,fashion') center center / cover no-repeat fixed;
            color: var(--primary-text-color);
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.6;
            position: relative;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 80px 70px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); /* Dicerahkan: Nilai alpha ditingkatkan */
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-card);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-subtle);
            max-width: 650px;
            width: 90%;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* Border juga dicerahkan agar serasi */
            animation: fadeInScale 0.8s ease-out forwards;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInScale {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.95);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-text-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2.8em;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.8px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.15em;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .buttons a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--primary-text-color);
            padding: 14px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 1.05em;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--button-login-bg), #38c172);
            border: none;
        }

        .buttons a.btn-register {
            background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--button-register-bg), #66afe9);
        }

        .buttons a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            filter: brightness(1.05);
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments for overall tighter feel */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 50px 50px;
                max-width: 550px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 1.1em;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            .buttons a {
                width: 80%;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 12px 25px;
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 40px 25px;
                width: 95%;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 0.95em;
                margin-bottom: 25px;
            }
            .buttons a {
                width: 90%;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 0.95em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Selamat Datang di Web Jaketku!</h1>
        <p>Temukan koleksi jaket terbaik untuk gaya Anda, mulai dari desain klasik hingga tren terbaru yang selalu up-to-date.</p>
        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="/login" class="btn-login">Masuk Sekarang</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn-register">Buat Akun Baru</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>